---
globs: **/*.*
alwaysApply: true
---

Context:
- Read `./docs/**/*.md` for project knowledge
- Use MCP tools when available (Context7, Playwright, pyscaf Docs)
- Consult `AGENTS.md` as the project constitution before major changes

Task Management:
- Create `_todo.md` at project root if not exists
- Track progress with `[X]` completed and `[ ]` pending
- ALWAYS refer to `_todo.md` when planning next step

File Operations:
- ALWAYS read file before writing
- ALWAYS check if file/folder exists before creating

Language:
- Respond in French
- Code comments and identifiers in English
